data.description: Heaven in the Country on 3.5 Acres--Rare opportunity.  Lovely two story with basement and wraparound porch.   All new paint inside and out.  Gleaming hardwood floors.  New carpet.  Remodeled kitchen with new appliances and granite countertops.  TWO MASTER BRs!! Fabulous inground pool and privacy fence.  Two car attached garage plus large detached workshop/one car garage.  Located in desirable Buckhorn High School district in New Market, Alabama.  Don't miss this great value!
